{"tid":92744,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"想買支鏡影人像 有無好介紹","createTime":"2017-01-23T23:02:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-27T01:59:27.000Z","uid":50225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3339813f12fe690c9d593d02f570bfa795a50916","tid":92744,"uid":50225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T23:02:49.000Z","msg":"我喺eos m3垃圾機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 醒原廠鏡 15-45mm f/3.5 好似喺<br />\n我想買支平平哋嘅鏡 影淺景深 我都知而支鏡都影到 但喺要張個頭擺滿哂成嗰畫面 景深先淺<br />\n我想平平地買支鏡影人像 好似咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/24/065609_5ab51645ef00368fb630718c7b7de19e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F24%2F065609_5ab51645ef00368fb630718c7b7de19e.jpg&h=4d577fff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBudget 大概$1000-$1500(窮撚)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔一定要原廠鏡 聽朋友講而支國產鏡都幾好 有無巴打買過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/24/070102_e6f7b34011d4c55c80ffbb1e5bf50c59.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F24%2F070102_e6f7b34011d4c55c80ffbb1e5bf50c59.jpg&h=ad4e0e64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n定喺建議我買翻原廠  新手乜都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"589b30d43d829b51c0a45513a5b964bc8b7c2e26","tid":92744,"uid":50225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T23:03:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我喺eos m3垃圾機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 配原廠鏡 15-45mm f/3.5 好似喺<br />\n我想買支平平哋嘅鏡 影淺景深 我都知而支鏡都影到 但喺要張個頭擺滿哂成嗰畫面 景深先淺<br />\n我想平平地買支鏡影人像 好似咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/24/065609_5ab51645ef00368fb630718c7b7de19e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F24%2F065609