咩 我都想買黎玩下<br />\n上對問個sales 話優惠$4500-5000 仲送多支鏡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都唔太識 不過我買咗翻嚟先知好多人都話垃圾嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過我就當我新手唔識 玩耐咗先再升級 對我嚟講暫時仲夠玩嘅"},{"pid":"6eec46621098c5731cfe0255b8c24cba8014040b","tid":92744,"uid":71341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T07:29:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fd2f46d8c6bb8fbfb2507a875a7c5f29f34faa74","tid":92744,"uid":50225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T07:31:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.hkyongnuo.com/c-detail.php?ID=390\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkyongnuo.com%2Fc-detail.php%3FID%3D390&d=AtWwe%2FdLOZlZPdCPsK%2F9awT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=ef1e84ab\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkyongnuo.com/c-detail.php?ID=390</a><br />\n<br />\n呢支完完全全係樓主你需要既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打而間國產鏡好唔好用？邊到有得買，我淨喺知taobo有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9615b52674c8c8117238c33e44ca9a0d751dccc","tid":92744,"uid":50225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T07:33:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>筆直1000-1500<br />\nCanon 50 1.8 stm <br />\n完</blockquote><br />\n水貨唔使一千添，樓記得買efs to efm 接環</blockquote><br />\nCanon機配canon鏡都要買接環？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申:咩都唔識"},{"pid":"933d163a5ffad22c5816b00dcf29c68b59e3b468","tid":92744,"uid":7119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T07:38:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>筆直1000-1500<br />\nCanon 50 1.8 stm <br />\n完</blockquote><br />\n水貨唔使一千添，樓記得買efs to efm 接環</blockquote><br />\nCanon機配canon鏡都要買接環？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申:咩都唔識</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n叫你配就配啦 <br />\n要問就問google"},{"pid":"1de8c13ab496d7790d96341ece803bbd84e47dfc","tid":92744,"uid":523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T08:44:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"http://www.hkyongnuo.com/c-detail.php?ID=390\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkyongnuo.com%2Fc-detail.php%3FID%3D390&d=AtWwe%2FdLOZlZPdCPsK%2F9awT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=ef1e84ab\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkyongnuo.com/c-detail.php?ID=390</a><br />\n<br />\n呢支完完全全係樓主你需要既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打而間國產鏡好唔好用？邊到有得買，我淨喺知taobo有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聽講抄到原廠鏡既八成 , 但價錢係原廠既五成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你畢直有限 無計<br />\nEos m 既接口叫 Efm <br />\n同單反用緊既Ef 接口唔同<br />\n所以要買一舊轉接環 大約500蚊"},{"pid":"466090e3ceb8cd114e46655e800f6373d6285e4d","tid":92744,"uid":50225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T09:53:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"http://www.hkyongnuo.com/c-detail.php?ID=390\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkyongnuo.com%2Fc-detail.php%3FID%3D390&d=AtWwe%2FdLOZlZPdCPsK%2F9awT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=ef1e84ab\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkyongnuo.com/c-detail.php?ID=390</a><br />\n<br />\n呢支完完全全係樓主你需要既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打而間國產鏡好唔好用？邊到有得買，我淨喺知taobo有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聽講抄到原廠鏡既八成 , 但價錢係原廠既五成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你畢直有限 無計<br />\nEos m 既接口叫 Efm <br />\n同單反用緊既Ef 接口唔同<br />\n所以要買一舊轉接環 大約500蚊</blockquote><br />\n轉接環都要$500<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過thx巴打 仲考慮緊買原廠鏡定國產鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b054e580f74354df39a9fd7c65bb4d2fd1979b5c","tid":92744,"uid":386